On Constitution Day & Citizenship Day, Agamim:
1. Welcomed Senator Melisa Franzen, Representative Heather Alstad Edelson, and Edina Mayor Jim Hovland to speak at our all-school assembly;
2. Received a Certificate of Award from The National Society of the Daughters of the American Revolution for recognizing Constitution Week;
3. Had all scholars, staff, and visitors sign our copy of The Preamble;
4. Watched a Naturalization Ceremony in the rotunda of the National Archives as a school; and
5. Distributed personal copies of the U.S. Constitution to every scholar.
